    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IMPORTANT!! We are having some issues about scaling. If you are a Mac user please change your resolution to 1280x800. If you are a Windows user please change your resolution to 1920x1080.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113060/extras/e773f6486ab0cc135f2c0b49274fedd6.avif?t=1736287151\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three musician friends are recording in their studio when everything changes. Utu, the evil god living in an old castle, attacks and throws the world into chaos. Now, the universe and time are in danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113060/extras/b9b43f7346f12d2a0147e326057b5a35.avif?t=1736287151\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Your World (I Own) is a 2D RPG game where you join this epic adventure. Utu’s evil plans trap Yaldız in Inanna's universe. Your goal is to explore these dangerous worlds, interact with NPCs, complete quests, and collect five powerful spellements through fun mini-games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113060/extras/9a0225f027f98e5a170a80715b2c703a.avif?t=1736287151\" width=592 height=339 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you collect all the spellements, you can reach Gece and restore order to the universes. Your friends' fate is in your hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113060/extras/b9b43f7346f12d2a0147e326057b5a35.avif?t=1736287151\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep story and rich world,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with NPCs and complete quests,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun mini-games and puzzles,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic 2D RPG gameplay and exploration,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful music and graphics,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the adventure in In Your World (I Own), collect the talismans, and save the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113060/extras/968a1f69efb86fdb34bb267553121bd4.avif?t=1736287151\" width=630 height=490 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press the space bar to skip dialogues and use the arrow keys to move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113060/extras/b9b43f7346f12d2a0147e326057b5a35.avif?t=1736287151\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have fun!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(ps: if you’d like to give an in depth feedback please don’t be shy and reach us at instagram: @https.tahta @suedakaraahmet or mail us: <a href=\"mailto:inyourworldiown@gmail.com)\">inyourworldiown@gmail.com)</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113060/extras/2c200505526df81fac8d225e021aee0b.avif?t=1736287151\" width=418 height=461 /></span></p>",
